data.description: Spacious & well-appointed two-story home in the established Redland Ridge neighborhood. The property offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms & 2 car attached garage. Interior features include open floor plan, hardwood floors in main living area, stairs, & formal dining room. Eat-in kitchen w/ceramic tile floors, granite counter tops, crown molding on cabinetry, stainless steel appliances & built-in microwave oven. Large Owner's retreat w/space for sitting area. Nice sized secondary bedrooms. Extended patio in backyard shaded by gorgeous mature oak trees. Roof replaced in 2017. Recently replaced carpet in all bedrooms.
